description:
Notes:

INCLUDES END CREDITS.

There is two-three minutes missing that arent really important of She's Not Afraid, i tried to find a YT video to go with my source to put that 2-3 mins back, but there was none. There is still audio for those 2 mins.

Its pretty good, audio is really clear, good bass, clear voices, and music scenes sound pretty good.
Ive had it on my laptop for about 2 months now, i thought someone already uploaded the movie.

But theirs wasnt like this one.


IMO: V/7 A/8
The concert scenes are a little bit blurry here and there.
But will hold over till the BR next month.


Runtime: 1hr 32mins.
